{"tid":1813613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到24歲就要破產","createTime":"2020-01-06T11:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T17:28:25.000Z","uid":183485,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f22d22220ccb88f9daa7b58ffa649568feb017","tid":1813613,"uid":183485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"本身自己返工﹐不過一直keep住大駛<br />\n成日駛突左就借﹐借借下就爆曬煲<br />\n一quit埋份工就出曬事﹐所有供款都找唔起<br />\n後來唯有死死氣同屋企攤牌﹐點知屋企話幫我唔到<br />\n帶左我去搵一個佢做律師既朋友﹐搵佢幫我搞破產。<br />\n聽日就要正式上去簽野﹐我一直係到諗﹐係﹐呢刻我係還唔起錢﹐<br />\n但﹐其實堆數夾埋都係20萬﹐係咪真係要破產呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我最淆既係我有幾條二線數﹐我睇過資料話呢d二線細財<br />\n唔理你老破定點﹐都一定會照追<br />\n真係好驚佢搞到我屋企人同身邊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183fc49bbd81fd75a2f3b77e6446e08b12356ab5","tid":1813613,"uid":90883,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"20萬咋喎 我嚴重過你都未諗破產"},{"pid":"b8536d27c748888bb7465129eccf904aad0c3174","tid":1813613,"uid":170979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"為20萬老破唔抵喎"},{"pid":"2b08daf7e187df3de4474d31a921a9f0c3dc831a","tid":1813613,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4dd537a2cfd68ac2ce057b2c3b33ab0335285a1f","tid":1813613,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"原來龍津美食係支那人開，唔怪之食完成日肚痛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cb0a9f235bb7f9f691adf417751bfea1c9fb001","tid":1813613,"uid":317107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"咁你呢刻又真係還唔到喎"},{"pid":"